msgid "Collabora Online Welcome"
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ Collabora Online"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h1:26-7
msgid "Explore The New {coolversion}"
msgstr "ສຳຫຼວດ {coolversion} ໃໝ່"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h2:27-7
#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h2:38-7
msgid "Collabora Online Development Edition"
msgstr "Collabora Online ສະບັບພັດທະນາ"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.p:28-7
msgid ""
"Enjoy the latest developments in online productivity, free for you to use, "
"to explore and to use with others in the browser. Various <a "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.collaboraonline.com/"
"solutions/collabora-office-android-ios/\">apps</a> are also available for "
"mobile."
msgstr ""
"ເພີດເພີນກັບການພັດທະນາຫຼ້າສຸດໃນດ້ານຜະລິດພາບອອນລາຍ, ໃຫ້ທ່ານໃຊ້ງານ, ສຳຫຼວດ ແລະ "
"ໃຊ້ກັບຜູ້ອື່ນໄດ້ຟຣີໃນບຣາວເຊີ. ມີ <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href="
"\"https://www.collaboraonline.com/solutions/collabora-office-android-ios/\""
">ແອັບ</a> ຕ່າງໆສຳລັບມືຖືອີກດ້ວຍ."

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h1:37-7
msgid "Discover All The Changes"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບການປ່ຽນແປງທັງໝົດ"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.p:39-7
msgid ""
"Check the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www."
"collaboraonline.com/code-25-04-release-notes/\">release notes</a> and learn "
"all about: The latest Collabora Online Development Edition, aimed at home "
"users and small teams."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບ <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www."
"collaboraonline.com/code-25-04-release-notes/\">ບັນທຶກການອອກລຸ້ນ</a> ແລະ "
"ຮຽນຮູ້ທັງໝົດກ່ຽວກັບ: Collabora Online ສະບັບພັດທະນາຫຼ້າສຸດ, "
"ເຊິ່ງແນໃສ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕາມບ້ານ ແລະ ທີມງານຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ."

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h1:48-7
msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າມາມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.h2:49-7
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://www.collaboraoffice.org/"
msgstr "https://www.collaboraonline.org/"

#: welcome/welcome.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.div.p:50-7
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Are you interested in contributing but don’t know where to start? Head over "
"to the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www."
"collaboraoffice.org/post/build-code/\">step-by-step instructions</a> and "
"build CODE from scratch. You can also help out with <a target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.collaboraoffice.org/post/translate/"
"\">translations</a> or by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" "
"href=\"https://www.collaboraoffice.org/post/filebugs/\">filing a bug "
"report</a> with all the essential steps on how to reproduce it."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສົນໃຈທີ່ຈະປະກອບສ່ວນແຕ່ບໍ່ຮູ້ວ່າຈະເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈາກໃສ? ໄປທີ່ <a target=\"_blank"
"\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.collaboraonline.org/post/build-code/\""
">ຄຳແນະນຳເທື່ອລະຂັ້ນຕອນ</a> ແລະ ສ້າງ CODE ຈາກຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ. "
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອດ້ວຍ <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https"
"://www.collaboraonline.org/post/translate/\">ການແປ</a> ຫຼື ໂດຍການ <a target="
"\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.collaboraonline.org/post/"
"filebugs/\">ລາຍງານບັກ</a> "
"ພ້ອມດ້ວຍຂັ້ນຕອນທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດກ່ຽວກັບວິທີເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດບັນຫາຊ້ຳ."

